FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our dog walking service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does your dog walking app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects dog owners with professional dog walkers in their area. Simply create a profile for your dog, schedule a walk, and we'll match you with an available walker.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are your dog walkers vetted and insured?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, all our dog walkers undergo a thorough background check and are fully insured. We prioritize the safety and well-being of your furry friends.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We offer flexible walk durations to suit your dog's needs. You can choose from 15, 30, or 60-minute walks when scheduling through the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I track my dog's walk in real-time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app features live GPS tracking, so you can see your dog's route and receive updates throughout the walk.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I need to cancel a scheduled walk?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We understand plans change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any cancellation fee. Later cancellations may incur a small fee.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Walking Service
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does your dog walking service work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with professional dog walkers in your area. Simply schedule a walk, and our vetted walkers will come to your home, take your furry friend for a stroll, and return them safely.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What safety measures do you have in place?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: All our dog walkers undergo thorough background checks and training. We also provide real-time GPS tracking of walks, photo updates, and insurance coverage for added peace of mind.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I book a dog walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Booking is easy through our user-friendly app. Select your preferred date, time, and walk duration, then choose from available walkers in your area. You can also set up recurring walks for regular exercise.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I need to cancel a scheduled walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We understand plans can change. You can cancel a scheduled walk through the app without penalty up to 24 hours before the appointment. For last-minute cancellations, a small fee may apply.
